# Start All Claw Projects Gateways

- [x] Stop `zeroclaw`, `NanoClaw`, and `picoclaw` (keeping `openclaw` running)
- [x] Restart `zeroclaw`, `NanoClaw`, and `picoclaw` from their project folders
- [x] Verify the status of the restarted gateways (zeroclaw: ✅, picoclaw: ✅, NanoClaw: ❌)
- [x] Determine how to run `nanobot` and execute it
- [x] Verify `nanobot` is running correctly (Port 18791: ✅)
